			<CASNumber>7647-01-0</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Hydrochloric acid, commonly known as muriatic acid, is a very acidic solution of hydrogen chloride gas dissolved in water. It is the aqueous solution of hydrogen chloride gas and the main component of gastric acid, an acid produced naturally in the human stomach to help digest food. Hydrochloric acid is synthetically produced for a variety of industrial and commercial applications. It is used in etching, water treatment, pH adjustment, pickling, acidizing, and ore treatment.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">盐酸，俗称乳酸，是氯化氢气体溶于水的酸性溶液。它是氯化氢气体的水溶液，也是胃酸的主要成分，胃酸是人体胃部为帮助消化食物而自然产生的一种酸。盐酸是为各种工业和商业应用而合成的。它可用于蚀刻、水处理、pH 值调节、酸洗、酸化和矿石处理。</common:generalComment>
